63
00:03:13,430 --> 00:03:16,150
Assuming we aren’t illegally stopped at
the border.

64
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:18,760
But as for Carrie Lam and her crocodile tears,

65
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,620
all I can say is,

66
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:22,120
see you later alligator,

67
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:24,080
in a while crocodile.

68
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,860
So what do you think of the growing protest
movement in Hong Kong?

69
